{"tid":1992110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家鋪天蓋地文宣鬧泛民攬炒！我哋要行動留住淺黃支持","createTime":"2020-04-28T02:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T06:05:33.000Z","uid":101392,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a0b4c28d862b979fcc705c5fa29148e7b6b37b","tid":1992110,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"觀塘： <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kzq2V3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzq2V3O.jpg&h=47768779&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n中環： <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/djGtRAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdjGtRAp.jpg&h=263ba73d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網上見到 香港各區都有<br />\n要諗計點樣留住淺黃 <br />\n同埋唔好俾對家拉攏到本身中立班人<br />\n<br />\n必也正名乎 <br />\n攬炒呢個term俾對家扭曲曬玩爛咗<br />\n我哋係咪要繼續用攬炒呢個term？係咪應該自稱攬炒派？<br />\n定係話對家先係攬炒 林鄭係「攬炒之母」？<br />\n我哋呢邊係守護香港核心價值嘅一派？<br />\n嗰陣我哋呢邊醫護罷工都係話「停止攬炒」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUU3FxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUU3FxF.jpg&h=ecc4f47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益"},{"pid":"a1bb9ac27a6745d7b28876471fb5eae5276eeaba","tid":1992110,"uid":122275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"攬炒權從來係對家決定"},{"pid":"58db2ef2fa0a7f9644cdae75a40a5e0b4c99d574","tid":1992110,"uid":101392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"要正視對家文宣<br />\n而家成個連登又喺度捉鬼內鬥話邊個泛民內會想縮、邊個唔肯攬炒、邊個唔肯初選<br />\n我哋呢邊內鬥分化之時<br />\n對家就集中火力搶中間票源<br />\n再係咁嚟緊九月輸硬"},{"pid":"70bbae3b4b41d959d10c7b89944558c15eb1548c","tid":1992110,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"而家捉鬼、內鬥、分化個勢有D似雨傘革命之後嗰幾年咁"},{"pid":"50015f251daff5f0e684328db1dd4fe67b978f31","tid":1992110,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"call食玩署洗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 